nodes.text: This alcoholic beverage was popular with Weequay pirates of Hondo Ohnaka. It was green in color. During the Weequay banquet on Florrum, Hondo's pirates were celebrating the capture of Count Dooku and this brew was served to Jedi Knights Obi-Wan Kenobi and Anakin Skywalker. Pirates tried to drug the Jedi, but Anakin and Obi-Wan used the Force to telekinetically swap their drinks with those of the flanking Weequay, who fell unconscious after imbibing.
At the end, they were still drugged by Hondo's pet Pilf Mukmuk.
